  "bio_raw": "Jannatul Ferdous Ruma joined the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB) as a Lecturer in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering. She completed her M.Sc. and B.Sc. in Computer Science and Engineering from North South University, Bangladesh. Before that, she worked as a full-time Lecturer at The International University of Scholars. She published five peer-reviewed journals and a multimodal Bengali NLG work. Her research interests are Natural Language Processing, Machine Learning, and Deep Learning.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Natural Language Processing (NLP), Machine Learning, Deep Learning."
  ],
